    <i>Mai 24, 2012&#160;</i> by Ana Constantin:<br/>
    Added inside surface orientation
  </li>
  <li>
    <i>April, 2012&#160;</i> by Mark Wesseling:<br/>
    Implemented.
  </li>
</ul>
</html>"));
end Wall_ASHRAE140;
